  "page": "Maester (mule)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\"><img alt=\"Dunk.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/50px-Dunk.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/75px-Dunk.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/100px-Dunk.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Maester</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\"><img alt=\"Dunk.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/50px-Dunk.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/75px-Dunk.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/78/Dunk.svg/100px-Dunk.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Dunk,_Egg,_and_Maester.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dunk, Egg, and Maester.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/83/Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg/350px-Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/83/Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg/525px-Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/83/Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg/700px-Dunk%2C_Egg%2C_and_Maester.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Dunk\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dunk\">Dunk</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>, and Maester, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://like-a-pimp-with-mjolnir.tumblr.com\">like-a-pimp-with-mjolnir</a> ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Mule\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mule\">Mule</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Gender</th><td>\nMale</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Maester</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Mule\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mule\">mule</a>, owned by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a>. The mule was a gift from the brother<sup id=\"cite_ref-Aemon_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Aemon-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> of Dunk's <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maester_(mule)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Duncan's old stot, <a href=\"/index.php/Chestnut\" title=\"Chestnut\">Chestnut</a>, died in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, during the desert crossing between the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince%27s_Pass\" title=\"Prince&#39;s Pass\">Prince's Pass</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Vaith\" title=\"Vaith\">Vaith</a>. As Chestnut had been Egg's steed, he and Dunk had to ride double on <a href=\"/index.php/Thunder\" title=\"Thunder\">Thunder</a>, as they had no other horses at the time. Eventually, Egg's brother, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon Targaryen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Aemon_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Aemon-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> a student at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, gave them a mule, named Maester.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Egg rode Maester when they traveled, and the mule also carried their equipment and purchases, such as <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> casks.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211&#160;AC</a>, after Ser Duncan did a service for Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>, she intended to pay him back with a gift of a horse. Although Dunk rejected her gift of <a href=\"/index.php/Flame\" title=\"Flame\">Flame</a>, he discovered that Egg was riding a new palfrey,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> named <a href=\"/index.php/Rain\" title=\"Rain\">Rain</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Afterwards, the mule was mainly used as a pack <a href=\"/index.php/Animal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Animal\">animal</a>, carrying Duncan's equipment.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212&#160;AC</a>, when Duncan lost a <a href=\"/index.php/Joust\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Joust\">tilt</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls_tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whitewalls tourney\">Whitewalls tourney</a> to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a>, and could not afford to pay the ransom for his <a href=\"/index.php/Thunder\" title=\"Thunder\">horse</a> and armor, Egg suggested that Dunk could ride Rain, and he would go back to riding Maester. However, Dunk rejected the idea, as that would mean returning in shame to Egg's father, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_Targaryen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maekar Targaryen\">Maekar Targaryen</a>, at <a href=\"/index.php/Summerhall\" title=\"Summerhall\">Summerhall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maester_(mule)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Aemon-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Aemon_2-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Aemon_2-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The mule was almost certainly given by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a>, as its name is <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a>, and no mention is made of Egg encountering any of his other brothers after the <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford_Tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ashford Tourney\">Ashford Tourney</a>. <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> states that <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Daeron</a> returned to <a href=\"/index.php/Summerhall\" title=\"Summerhall\">Summerhall</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion</a> was in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, whereas he and Dunk met Aemon in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, after they left <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maester_(mule)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403172958\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.124 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.405 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 713/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10403/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6807/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1129/2097152 bytes\nHighes